<hr data-start="909" data-end="912">
<h1 data-section-id="11rmjwm" data-start="914" data-end="959">🚀 Next Level Upgrades (Highly Recommended)</h1>
<p data-start="961" data-end="1012">If you want <strong data-start="973" data-end="997">REAL customers daily</strong>, do this next:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="r74ksn" data-start="1014" data-end="1059">1. Move from localStorage → REAL database</h3>
<p data-start="1060" data-end="1064">Use:</p>
<ul data-start="1065" data-end="1105">
<li data-section-id="kcebai" data-start="1065" data-end="1082">
<p data-start="1067" data-end="1082">Firebase (easy)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="qp7z4o" data-start="1083" data-end="1105">
<p data-start="1085" data-end="1105">or Google Sheets API</p>
</li>
</ul>
